<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246359>
    dc:description "FIGURE 28. Final instar caterpillars of Gegenes niso brevicornis. 1, newly moulted, dorsal view, collected as n- 2 instar caterpillar on maize, Kyuna Estate, Nairobi; moulted to final instar 17. xi.; photographed 17. xi., 22 mm; pupated 26. xi.; ref. 88 / 110; 2, detail of head, anterior view; as (1); 3, detail of head, anterolateral view, collected as n- 3 instar caterpillar on Leersia hexandra, Kyuna Estate, Nairobi, 30. i. 1990; moulted to final instar 6 – 9. ii.; photographed 10. ii., 22 mm; pupated 20. ii.; ref. 90 / 6 G." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246359/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.246360>
    dc:description "FIGURE 29. Pupa of Gegenes niso brevicornis, collected as n- 3 instar caterpillar on Leersia hexandra, Kyuna Estate, Nairobi, 30. i. 1990; pupated 20. ii.; photographed 22. ii., 21 mm; male emerged 5. iii.; ref. 90 / 6 G." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/246360/files/figure.png" ;
